{
  "stem": "6277.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we would see it coming, the-- the-- the-- the-- the smoke from the hole.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We weren't, for a long time, there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And from-- from there, we went to-- they took us to Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in beginning of September or end of August, we arrived in Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there began another chapter of our prisoner's life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Buchenwald was a different camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Buchenwald, the inside power was in the hand of the political prisoners.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the inside condition were better, but not for all of the prisoners.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Jewish, us, when we came in, when we arrived, they put us not in the barracks, but on the field.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were a special-- a [? special ?] part of the camp who was, they called it quarantine.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So the people who arrived, us, they put it in the quarantine camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there wasn't barracks, nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We would sleep outside.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was one small house-- a house or barrack, very small one without-- without windows, only two doors on both sides.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they could-- We were about-- about 1,000 people, let's say.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there could sleep only 100, if they were as sardines inside [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we would sleep outside.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was very cold.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And daytime, they would take us to the quarry, where Austrian-Jewish worked.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the guards around were Ukraine, from Ukraine, Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And there we would-- we would take a stone-- every one of us had to take a stone, go-- go down in the quarry, take a stone, come up, and then we make a group and go to the camp.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was-- we worked as-- it came to your minds that we were are the same as the slaves from Egypt.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And so we would go from one side to the other.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
